Html: On the previous version a genetic solving would give 1-2k more DPS now it's almost the same. Also the sequence reconstruction would make more sense. Now e.g. Moonwell Chalice appears to not be aligned with other cooldowns.

If you're comparing against 4.2.4c there should be no change I think. Note that genetic solver (similar to the optimizer) is not guaranteed to get the optimum every time, try to run it several times to see if it was just a fluke.
